HEADWORD: Irresponsibly
<hw>Ir`re*spon"si*bly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>So as not
to be responsible.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In an irresponsible{2} manner; without due care or
